## Features

- ✅ **Properties-based Configuration**: Uses `application.properties` for configuration
- ✅ **Eureka Integration**: Automatic service registration and discovery
- ✅ **Health Checks**: Built-in health check endpoint
- ✅ **HTTP Server**: FastHTTP server with routing
- ✅ **Graceful Shutdown**: Proper cleanup on shutdown

## Eureka Service Registry

This service automatically registers with Eureka when `eureka.enabled=true`.

### Service Discovery

To discover other services, use the Eureka client:

```go
import "github.com/fluxorio/fluxor/pkg/eureka"

client := eureka.NewClient(eureka.DefaultClientConfig("http://localhost:8761", instance))
instances, err := client.Discover(ctx, "other-service")
```

